  "remarks": "\nAs a member of GRU Unit 26165, Artem Adreyevich MALYSHEV has been involved in relevant cyber activity in that he was responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting the commissioning, planning or preparation of relevant cyber activity. Such activity that Artem Andreyevich MALYSHEV has been involved in, or is intended to undermine, the integrity, prosperity or security of the United Kingdom or a country other than the United Kingdom. \n",
